title: Dige
text: Dige () is a town in the south of <a href="Shandong">Shandong</a> province, People's Republic of China, bordering <a href="Jiangsu">Jiangsu</a> province to the south, and located in the southeast corner of <a href="Zaozhuang">Zaozhuang</a> City. It is under the administration of <a href="Yicheng%20District%2C%20Zaozhuang">Yicheng District</a> and is east-southeast of downtown Zaozhuang. In March 2001, the former Ganlugou Township () was merged into the town's administrative area.
